Package: bbcnews
Type: Package
Title: BBC News article text analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Angelina Khatiwada
Maintainer: Angelina Khatiwada <linakhatiwada@gmail.com>
Description: Scrap article text from BBC News website (https://www.bbc.com/news/). 
             Clean and transform text. 
             Build a dataframe with the most frequent words. 
             Plot the most frequent words with wordcloud. 
             Find terms associations. Analyze sentiment distribution across the article
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    rvest,
    xml2,
    tm,
    SnowballC,
    wordcloud,
    sentimentr,
    ggplot2,
    RColorBrewer,
    utils,
    devtools,
    dplyr,
    magrittr
Suggests:
